      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 15,
      "message": "Hi Kiran, \nThe API is set in the Istio-operator.\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/demo/+/92409/3/vnfs/DAaaS/deploy/00-init/istio/istio-operator/templates/operator-istio-1.2-crd.yaml\n\nSteps in deployment\n1. The operator pods come up\n2. Depending on the configuration as per this patch, the operator deploys specific istio pods. The API s are defined in the operator.\n\nIs that what you were looking for?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3261,
        "name": "Pramod",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "pramod.raghavendra.jayathirth@intel.com",
        "username": "Pramod"
